<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.8.4">
<l>pārttaṟ kāyaṉṟu pāra taṅkaicey tiṭṭu veṉṟapa rañcuṭar</l>
<l>kōttaṅ kāyartam pāṭi yilkura vaipi ṇaintaveṅ kōvala</l>
<l>nēttu vārttamma ṉattuḷ ḷāṉiṭa ventai</l>
<l>mēviya vempirāṉ</l>
<l>tīrtta nīrttaṭañ cōlai cūḻtiru vēṅka ṭamaṭai neñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] heart, take refuge at Tiruvēṅkaṭam,</l>
<l rend="indent">encircled by groves with ponds of sacred waters</l>
<l>Of our lord who dwells in Iṭaventai, the one in the minds</l>
<l rend="indent">of those who praise [him],</l>
<l>Our cowherd who joined in the kuravai [dance] clasping hands</l>
<l rend="indent">there in the herders’ village,</l>
<l>The great light who was victorious, decisively aiding</l>
<l rend="indent">in the Bhārata [War] then for the sake of Pārtha.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
